  37,156,Or do you have ňĻanyňļ compelling proof
  37,157,"Then bring ňĻusňļ your scripture, if what you say is true"
  37,158,They have also established a ňĻmaritalňļ relationship between Him and the jinn. Yet the jinn ňĻthemselvesňļ know well that such people will certainly be brought ňĻfor punishmentňļ
